column5: With my annual trip to lotw approaching I need some info. I just purchased a different vehicle and was informed that the title might not be here in time to license it before our trip. My question is if I have all the paper work,proof of purchase, insurance,etc., will that be enough to get us across the border.

The following Canadian government web site provides instructions to follow for information about visiting Canada (e.g. contact a consulate office). Scroll down to the hyperlink for consulate offices and you'll be able to access information on how to contact US consulate offices (e.g. telephone, email).http://www.cic.gc.ca/english/visit/index.html
